.TH NOTFLIX "1" "December 2025" "202602020740-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
notflix \- Search and stream torrents with webtorrent
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B notflix
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] [\fI\,SEARCH_QUERY\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B notflix
is a tool that searches for magnet links and streams content directly using webtorrent. It provides a Netflix-like experience for streaming torrent content without needing to download the entire file first.
.PP
The script searches various torrent indexers and uses webtorrent to stream the selected content to a media player.
